modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod reduces the harvest you get back from blocks like cloth, pipes, polymers, mech parts and electric parts.
modDescription:
JaxTeller718 seen some talk from people about how harvesting from blocks can give a lot of extra resources. This 7 Days to Die mod reduces the harvest you get back from blocks like [cloth](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-clothing/), pipes, polymers, mech parts and [electric](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-electricity/) parts.

[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/JaxTeller718_Modlets_Stable/tree/master/JaxTeller718_ReducedHarvestResources)

If you appreciate JaxTeller718’s work here feel free to use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/FrankCirabisiJr) to show support.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/8098-jaxteller718-modlet-collection/).

**Credits:** [JaxTeller718](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/jaxteller718/)
